ata":{"id":"dhuenrn7v1c0","created":1776325000222,"text":"基于体系结构的软件设计","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuer5dc0ao0","created":1776325265191,"text":"由构成体系结构的商业、质量和功能需求的组合驱动","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhueruf4d3k0","created":1776325319719,"text":"3个基础","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuerwrmey80","created":1776325324829,"text":"功能分解","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhues1ijlrs0","created":1776325335163,"text":"通过选择体系结构风格来实现质量和商业需求","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhues9yypts0","created":1776325353571,"text":"使用软件模版","font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhuevt5kjz40","created":1776325630421,"text":"基于体系结构的开发","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuew5032vc0","created":1776325656211,"text":"子过程（许设温敷试验）","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuewjlv0co0","created":1776325688003,"text":"需求","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuex592fdk0","created":1776325735118,"text":"系统质量目标","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuex8d462g0","created":1776325741894,"text":"商业目标","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuexb590w00","created":1776325747948,"text":"开发人员商业目标","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhuewl9mlio0","created":1776325691617,"text":"设计","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhvarimpnu80","created":1776415569574,"text":"提出模型","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhvarkgluao0","created":1776415573558,"text":"映射构件","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhvarmmft3c0","created":1776415578264,"text":"分析构件相互作用","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhvarq30kzk0","created":1776415585797,"text":"产生架构","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhvars2ln8g0","created":1776415590125,"text":"架构评审","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhuewmidp5s0","created":1776325694323,"text":"文档化","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuey75rj6g0","created":1776325817636,"text":"输出","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuey82fim00","created":1776325819612,"text":"体系结构规格说明书","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhueyfm5bd40","created":1776325836041,"text":"测试质量设计说明书","font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhuewnmpg0g0","created":1776325696761,"text":"复审","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuewr0m3so0","created":1776325704132,"text":"实现","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuexvlaa6o0","created":1776325792454,"text":"演化","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuezj3v6iw0","created":1776325922007,"text":"需求变化归类","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuezoiysrs0","created":1776325933804,"text":"制定演化计划","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuf03g6zt40","created":1776325966288,"text":"修改/增加/扇出构件","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuf07426qo0","created":1776325974262,"text":"更新构件的相互作用","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuf0by6ceg0","created":1776325984790,"text":"构件组装与测试","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuf0f0sth40","created":1776325991479,"text":"技术评审","font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhuhs5b1jrs0","created":1776333806747,"text":"定义","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuhs6fwyig0","created":1776333809218,"text":"ABSD 方法是一个自顶向下，递归细化的方法，软件系\n统的体系结构通过该方法得到细化，直到能产生软件构\n件和类。在最顶层，系统被分解为若干概念子系统和一\n个或若干个软件模板。在第 2 层，概念子系统又被分解\n成概念构件和一个或若干个附加软件模板。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-151,"y":4},"font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhuf92m8rco0","created":1776326669755,"text":"软件架构风格","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuf96cbrqg0","created":1776326677862,"text":"概念","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuf97jof1c0","created":1776326680484,"text":"描述某一特定应用领域中系统组织方式的惯用模式。体\n系结构风格定义一个系统家族，即一个体系结构定义一\n个词汇表和一组约束。词汇表中包含一些构件和连接\n件，而这组约束指出系统是如何将这些构件和连接件组\n合起来的。体系结构风格反映了领域中众多系统所共有\n的结构和语义特性，并指导如何将各个模块和子系统有\n效地组织成一个完整的系统。","layout_left_offset":{"x":-165,"y":-61},"font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhufbg23h1k0","created":1776326855740,"text":"分类","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhufrtfhewg0","created":1776328138674,"text":"数据流风格","expandState":"expand","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhufbgxr0ig0","created":1776326857654,"text":"批处理风格","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhufcfnq2h40","created":1776326933235,"text":"每个步骤是一个单独的程序，每一步必须在前一步结束\n后才能开始，并且数据必须是完成的，以整体的方式传\n递。它的基本构件是独立的应用程序，连接件是某种类\n型的媒介。","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhufbz9oq0g0","created":1776326897558,"text":"管道/过滤器风格","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhufqmpjmns0","created":1776328045681,"text":"一个步骤的输出是另一个步骤的输入，可以并行处理；\n基本构件是过滤器，连接件是数据流传输管道。","font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhufshmr5n40","created":1776328191356,"text":"调用/返回风格","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhufskvk7vc0","created":1776328198419,"text":"主/子程序风格","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhufsqtpp280","created":1776328211368,"text":"面向对象风格","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhufsu4y97s0","created":1776328218578,"text":"层次结构风格","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhuft7kp80w0","created":1776328247829,"text":"客户端/服务器风格","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhug0ypb5vc0","created":1776328855430,"text":"以数据为中心","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhug11q5wdk0","created":1776328862012,"text":"仓库风格","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhug1etnfw80","created":1776328890521,"text":"中央数据结构","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhvc3rbl52w0","created":1776419349972,"text":"独立构件","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhug16ag2g80","created":1776328871945,"text":"黑板风格","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhug2hyxmyw0","created":1776328975735,"text":"虚拟机","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhug2o4yrkw0","created":1776328989160,"text":"解释器风格","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhug2t4tw1c0","created":1776329000036,"text":"规则系统风格","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhvaimg4m7k0","created":1776414872605,"text":"知识/规则库","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhvaiqumnjk0","created":1776414882189,"text":"规则/数据选择器","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhvaiw2rayw0","created":1776414893565,"text":"规则引擎","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhvaixn2pk80","created":1776414896970,"text":"工作内存","font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhug2z8zcjs0","created":1776329013347,"text":"独立构件","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhug327n5co0","created":1776329019797,"text":"进程通信风格","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhug36oxqbc0","created":1776329029550,"text":"事件驱动/隐式调用风格","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhug3kdwzps0","created":1776329059358,"text":"c2风格（并行）","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhug3vnqriw0","created":1776329083897,"text":"构件和连接件都有顶部和底部","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhug40p8rxc0","created":1776329094872,"text":"构件之间不允许直接连接","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhug46g63ow0","created":1776329107384,"text":"连接件可以连接任意数量的构件和其它连接件","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhug4gdeyxk0","created":1776329128985,"text":"当两个连接件直接相连时，必须一个底部连接到另一个的顶部","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhug4vnz9fc0","created":1776329162275,"text":"闭环控制风格","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhug5451y880","created":1776329180722,"text":"比如空调控温度，定速巡航","font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhvakm2uzyw0","created":1776415028531,"text":"架构描述语言ADL","progress":null,"font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhvakrorhds0","created":1776415040740,"text":"构件（执行特定功能的独立单元）","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhval00hk3s0","created":1776415058863,"text":"连接件（定义构件之前如何通信）","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhval4m95p40","created":1776415068886,"text":"架构配置（描述构件与连接件的组织方式）","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhug5ojrzts0","created":1776329225148,"text":"软件架构复用","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhuhvk1mhdk0","created":1776334073921,"text":"是指在多个软件系统或项目中重复使用已有的架构设\n计、组件、模式、技术或构件，以提高开发效率、降低\n成本、提高软件质量和可维护性；主要分为机会复用和\n系统复用；","layout_left_offset":{"x":-51,"y":4},"font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv3zm9rhzc0","created":1776396456642,"text":"软件产品线","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv3zreql5c0","created":1776396467827,"text":"核心资产库：设计方案及其文档、用户手册、项目管\n理的历史记录、软件测试计划和测试用例","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv41cfe24g0","created":1776396591943,"text":"基本过程","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv41ejui8w0","created":1776396596566,"text":"构造/获取可复用的资产","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv41iqs1i80","created":1776396605692,"text":"管理可复用资产","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv41mtdp3k0","created":1776396614556,"text":"使用可复用资产","font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv423ykimg0","created":1776396651875,"text":"特定领域软件体系结构 - DSSA\n核心要素：领域参考模型、参考\n需求、参考架构","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv434kfd5k0","created":1776396731561,"text":"分类","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv435isnvk0","created":1776396733639,"text":"垂直域，只能应用于成熟、稳定的领域","font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhv438cz0kw0","created":1776396739818,"text":"水平域","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv43qy8jm80","created":1776396780285,"text":"基本活动","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhv43tm7vyo0","created":1776396786089,"text":"领域分析","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhxtszyir5c0","created":1776672406659,"text":"获得领域模型，描述共同需求","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv43uw24zc0","created":1776396788861,"text":"领域设计","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhxtt8x2g9k0","created":1776672426162,"text":"获得DSSA","font-size":24},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv43w35myg0","created":1776396791467,"text":"领域实现","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhxttdysky80","created":1776672437150,"text":"根据领域模型和DSSA，开发和组织重用信息","font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhv4